17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 1-109, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 1-109. A. For all public schools in Oklahoma this
20 state, school shall actually be in session and classroom instruction
21 offered:
22 1. For not less than one hundred eighty (180) days; or
23 2. For not less than one thousand eighty (1,080) hours each
24 school year, if a district board of education adopts a school-hours
